            <h2>Understanding Body Fat</h2>
            <p>
                Body fat, also known as adipose tissue, plays a vital role in the human body. It serves as an energy reserve, provides insulation, and cushions vital organs. However, maintaining an optimal body fat percentage is essential for overall health and athletic performance.
            </p>
            <p>
