                <li><strong>Bioelectrical Impedance Analysis (BIA):</strong> Measures the resistance of body tissues to electrical currents to estimate body fat.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Our advanced Body Fat Calculator primarily utilizes the Navy Method, which offers a balance between accuracy and ease of measurement.
            </p>
            
            <h3>Factors Affecting Body Fat Percentage</h3>
